== IUST E-Commerce project

* Based on Ruby programming language
* A Ruby on Rails based website for e-commerce solutions

== Specifications

* Ruby version : 1.9
* Rails version: 3.2.13
* IDE used for project: JetBrains Rubymine 5.4

== Contributors

